Content usage

The content created by the participants can be used in society and in the classroom for education and community development. The designed materials can also be used to assist learners to transition to other teaching software and teaching content including Virtual Worlds and virtual reality by participants in a school setting. It also can be used to assist with the varying needs of the students in the community.
